dc:description: Buff clay with red to brown glaze.  Long flat nozzle comes to almost a point, separated from broad flat rim by groove.  Small plain concave discus separated from plain rim by groove and outer edge slightly higher than rim.  No handle.  Plain flat reverse.  Stamp, imprint of right foot, containing illegible raised letters.
